  "texts": [
    "The chatbot provided an efficient step-by-step solution when given the equation for calculating the kinetic energy given to electrons by incident light.",
    "The chatbot calculated the kinetic energy to be 9.6 × 10 -19 Joules, using the formula K.E.",
    "= eV0, where e represents the charge of an electron and V0 is the stopping potential.",
    "Collaborative discussions with groups and teachers can help ensure the accuracy of the solution.",
    "Individuals can analyze the problem-solving strategy and collectively verify the calculation steps by sharing the chatbot's response in a group setting."
